lusterRoleBinding) |\n355: | `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac-router.yaml` | Create | ~50 | Router RBAC (conditional) |\n356: | `manifests/charts/base/templates/volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` | Create | ~60 | Volcano scheduler (conditional) |\n357: | `manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml` | Create | ~150 | AgentRuntime CRD |\n358: | `manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml` | Create | ~150 | CodeInterpreter CRD |\n359: \n360: ---\n361: \n362: ## Implementation Notes\n363: \n364: ### Chart.yaml Structure\n365: \n366: ```yaml\n367: apiVersion: v1\n368: name: agentcube\n369: description: A Helm chart for AgentCube\n370: type: application\n371: version: 0.1.0\n372: appVersion: 1.0.0\n373: keywords:\n374:   - agentcube\n375:   - kubernetes\n376:   - sandbox\n377:   - ai-agents\n378: maintainers:\n379:   - name: volcano-sh\n380:     email: volcano-sh@example.com\n381: sources:\n382:   - https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube\n383: ```\n384: \n385: ### _helpers.tpl Named Templates\n386: \n387: ```yaml\n388: {{- define \"agentcube.name\" -}}\n389: {{- default .Chart.Name .Values.nameOverride | trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\" -}}\n390: {{- end -}}\n391: \n392: {{- define \"agentcube.fullname\" -}}\n393: {{- if .Values.fullnameOverride -}}\n394: {{- .Values.fullnameOverride | trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\" -}}\n395: {{- else -}}\n396: {{- $name := default .Chart.Name .Values.nameOverride -}}\n397: {{- if contains $name .Release.Name -}}\n398: {{- .Release.Name | trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\" -}}\n399: {{- else -}}\n400: {{- printf \"%s-%s\" .Release.Name $name | trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\" -}}\n401: {{- end -}}\n402: {{- end -}}\n403: {{- end -}}\n404: \n405: {{- define \"agentcube.labels\" -}}\n406: app.kubernetes.io/name: {{ include \"agentcube.name\" . }}\n407: app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\n408: app.kubernetes.io/version: {{ .Chart.AppVersion }}\n409: app.kubernetes.io/managed-by: {{ .Release.Service }}\n410: {{- end -}}\n411: \n412: {{- define \"agentcube.selectorLabels\" -}}\n413: app: {{ include \"agentcube.name\" . }}\n414: {{- end -}}\n415: ```\n416: \n417: ### Required Value Validation Pattern\n418: \n419: ```yaml\n420: {{- if not .Values.redis.addr }}\n421: {{- fail \"redis.addr must be provided\" }}\n422: {{- end }}\n423: ```\n424: \n425: ### Conditional RBAC Rendering Pattern\n426: \n427: ```yaml\n428: {{- if .Values.router.rbac.create }}\n429: {{- if not .Values.router.serviceAccountName }}\n430: {{- fail \"router.serviceAccountName must be set when router.rbac.create is true\" }}\n431: {{- end }}\n432: # RBAC resources...\n433: {{- end }}\n434: ```\n435: \n436: ---\n437: \n438: ## Implementation Timeline\n439: \n440: | Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n441: |-------|-------|--------|------------|\n442: | Phase 1: Foundation | T1.1-T1.3 | Pending | 0% |\n443: | Phase 2: WorkloadManager | T2.1-T2.8 | Pending | 0% |\n444: | Phase 3: Router | T3.1-T3.9 | Pending | 0% |\n445: | Phase 4: RBAC | T4.1-T4.5 | Pending | 0% |\n446: | Phase 5: Volcano Scheduler | T5.1-T5.3 | Pending | 0% |\n447: | Phase 6: CRDs | T6.1-T6.4 | Pending | 0% |\n448: | Phase 7: Validation | T7.1-T7.3 | Pending | 0% |\n449: | Phase 8: Tests | T8.1-T8.8 | Pending | 0% |\n450: \n451: **Total Progress: 0% Complete (0/47 tasks)**\n452: \n453: ---\n454: \n455: ## References\n456: \n457: - Design: `changes/AR-030/design.md`\n458: - Delta Spec: `changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md`\n459: - Proposal: `changes/AR-030/proposal.md`\n460: - deployment/design.md — Reference implementation details\n461: - ci-cd/design.md — E2E Helm usage patterns\n462: - Helm 3 Documentation — Chart structure, templates, values best practices\n463: - Kubernetes API Reference — Deployment, Service, RBAC schemas\n\n(End of file - total 463 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-030 — Helm Chart 模板与 Values Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-030 — H